(6, 'Quick BMW Part Finder CodeAlong', 'I need to find a part for my car but there are over 150 pages to look through. Let’s use a little dev tools and JS magic to make this faster! I also found out that $430 is for the entire door kit -the little plastic piece I need is only $100 so I will be starting a GoFundMe to raise awareness and funds', 'assets/course_videos/696e73742d314f32385f24312d746b36323132333538.MP4', 'assets/playlist_thumbnail/696e73742d314f32385f24312d746b36323132333538.jpg', 0, 1, '2019-01-07 21:28:47', NULL, NULL, NULL, 6, NULL, 1),
(7, 'Introduction to SEO', 'Introduction to this SEO Training 2019 Course for Wordpress Website. Learn the basics of Search Engine Optimization (SEO) with me so your site can be found on Google, Bing and other search engines.', 'assets/course_videos/696e73742d314f32385f24322d746b36323135383135.mp4', 'assets/playlist_thumbnail/696e73742d314f32385f24322d746b36323135383135.jpg', 1, 2, '2019-01-07 21:58:36', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 1),
(8, 'Keyword Research', 'Finding the best tools for keyword research doesn\'t have to be hard, or expensive! You can also get a long tail keyword research tool right insight of Google search. There are so many SEO techniques <br />\r\nWhy long tail keywords bring in better conversions?<br />\r\n', 'assets/course_videos/696e73742d314f32385f24322d746b36323230303431.mp4', 'assets/playlist_thumbnail/696e73742d314f32385f24322d746b36323230303431.jpg', 1, 2, '2019-01-07 22:01:26', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, NULL, 1),
(9, 'Introduction to SEO', 'This tutorial shows how to easily improve your technical SEO using Wordpress plugins, configurations, and simple strategies. <br />\r\nWhy Technical Factors Matter in SEO? <br />\r\nExistence of Meta Description , Existence of H tags , H tags in User Experience + Brand Factor , Domain SEO Visibility , Keyword in Domain Name , HTTPS , Technical SEO Quiz 1, Search Volume of , domain Name , Ratio of HomePages , Domain is .COM, Flash Content, URL Length , File Size , Site or Page Speed, Wrap Up, Implement Technical SEO Factors in your website.', 'assets/course_videos/696e73742d314f32385f24322d746b36323230393135.mp4', 'assets/playlist_thumbnail/696e73742d314f32385f24322d746b36323230393135.jpg', 0, 2, '2019-01-07 22:15:19', NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, 1),
(10, 'Get indexed by search engine faster', 'In this video, I am going to show you, how to get search engines to crawl and index your site faster.\r\nCreate A Sitemap For Your Website<br />\r\nIf you can\'t see XML sitemaps on Yoast SEO, Do this...<br />\r\nLinks to all sites discussed in this section<br />\r\nHow To Add Your Website To Google Search Console<br />\r\nHow To Add Sitemap Of Your Site To Google Search Console<br />\r\nHow To Add “www” Version Of Your Domain To Search Console<br />\r\nCreate a Sitemap and Submit to Google<br />\r\nHow To Add Your Website & Sitemap To Bing<br />\r\nHow To Add Your Website & Sitemap To Yandex<br />\r\nHow to Claim website in Alexa', 'assets/course_videos/696e73742d314f32385f24322d746b36323231363432.mp4', 'assets/playlist_thumbnail/696e73742d314f32385f24322d746b36323231363432.jpg', 0, 2, '2019-01-07 22:16:59', NULL, NULL, NULL, 4, NULL, 1),
(11, 'Future SEO Factors', 'In this video, I am going to show you, how to get search engines to crawl and index your site faster.<br/>\r\nWhy User Experience Matters in SEO?<br/>\r\nHow many Internal Links should you add in your post? <br/>\r\nHow many images should you add in your post? <br/>\r\nHow to add copyright-free related images to your post for free? <br/>\r\nVideos Integration <br/>\r\nHow to add related videos? <br/>\r\nResponsive Design <br/>\r\nHow to Change to a responsive WordPress theme for free? <br/>\r\nFont Size <br/>\r\nInteractive Elements <br/>\r\nHow to add interactive elements to your WordPress website <br/>\r\nUnordered Lists <br/>\r\nAdvertisements <br/>\r\nUser Signals <br/>\r\nClick Through Rate <br/>\r\nHow to Headings & Meta Description that induce Users to click on Google Search? <br/>\r\n   Test your Heading Score with these Analysers <br/>\r\nHow to add Rich Snippets to your Website?<br/> \r\n\r\n', 'assets/course_videos/696e73742d314f32385f24322d746b36323231383335.mp4', 'assets/playlist_thumbnail/696e73742d314f32385f24322d746b36323231383335.jpg', 0, 2, '2019-01-07 22:19:15', NULL, NULL, NULL, 5, NULL, 1),
(12, 'Creating Shareable Content', 'Amazing content is always the KING in search engine optimization. Creating amazing and shareable content is a smart way to generating more and more natural backlinks to our website or blog. Research often and keep your content always fresh and updated.', 'assets/course_videos/696e73742d314f31385f24342d746b3130313330303335.mp4', 'assets/playlist_thumbnail/696e73742d314f31385f24342d746b3130313330303335.jpg', 1, 4, '2019-01-11 13:01:46', NULL, NULL, '00:03:40', 1, NULL, 1),
(13, 'Influencer Outreach', 'If you have created any kind of content which is share worthy, then don’t hesitate to reach out influencers in your industry. Tell them to check your blog and ask for link backs from their blog. Make sure you get the links from completely relevant domains.', 'assets/course_videos/696e73742d314f31385f24342d746b3130313331343031.mp4', 'assets/playlist_thumbnail/696e73742d314f31385f24342d746b3130313331343031.jpg', 0, 4, '2019-01-11 13:15:41', NULL, NULL, '00:03:40', 2, NULL, 1),
(14, 'Social Media Engagement', 'A major Off-page SEO technique is social media engagement. If you want to make your business, website or blog popular, engage with people on multiple social media platforms. Social media presence will help grow your business and also help you get more back links.', 'assets/course_videos/696e73742d314f31385f24342d746b3130313334343237.mp4', 'assets/playlist_thumbnail/696e73742d314f31385f24342d746b3130313334343237.jpg', 0, 4, '2019-01-11 13:46:36', NULL, NULL, '00:01:47', 3, NULL, 1),
